健康免責聲明 Health Disclaimer

本資料庫提供的更年期體重管理資訊（荷爾蒙變化、飲食建議、症狀緩解策略）
僅供一般教育和資訊參考，不構成醫療建議、診斷或治療。

更年期症狀因人而異，且可能與其他健康狀況重疊。任何更年期相關的健康問題
（荷爾蒙補充療法、骨質疏鬆治療等），請諮詢婦產科或家醫科醫師。

Menopause-related nutritional and weight management information in this database
is for general educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice.
Menopause symptoms vary individually and may overlap with other health conditions.
Please consult a qualified healthcare professional for personalized guidance.
